STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Douglas A. FLANNEL, Defendant-Petitioner. C-1024 September Term 2017
080695 Supreme Court of New Jersey. July 6, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005371-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
